      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PANAMA JAN (6) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (22.62) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Better than latest and can atone here. PLUTOCRACY (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (26.40) in a Special conditions H at Ballarat. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from six starts. Should be in this for a long way. SAINT FINNIE (3) turned in a plain run last time when eighth at this track over 390m behind Paw Amaran (23.12) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Can figure in the finish. FOZZY'S BOY (1) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
